{
  "id": "bad_moon_rising",
  "name": {
    "en": "Bad Moon Rising",
    "cn": "黯月初升"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "The sun is swallowed by a jagged horizon as another winter's day surrenders to the night. Flecks of orange and red decay into deeper browns, the forest transforming in silent anticipation of the coming snow.",
    "cn": "冬日的暮色渐近，太阳被盘陀的天际线所吞噬，橙红的枫叶被黑色斑点逐渐侵蚀，森林无声地期待着雪花将至。"
  },
